<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem; background-color: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px; color: #212529;">

  <h2 style="margin-top: 0;">Hello <%= @resource.email %></h2>

  <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
    We're reaching out to let you know that your password was recently changed.
  </p>

  <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
    If you made this change, no further action is needed.
  </p>

  <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #dc3545;">
    If you did <strong>not</strong> change your password, please <a href="mailto:support@example.com" style="color: #dc3545; text-decoration: underline;">contact support</a> immediately.
  </p>

  <p style="margin-top: 3rem; font-size: 14px; color: #6c757d;">
    Thank you,<br>
    <strong>The Access Control App Team</strong>
  </p>

</div>
